{"type":"message","id":"25944bca","parentId":"a352bd5a","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:56:22.507Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在我了解了OpenClaw的配置。让我给用户一个完整的迁移指南。\n\n需要迁移的内容包括：\n1. ~/.openclaw 目录（配置、插件、记忆等）\n2. 全局 npm 包（如 skillhub）\n3. 可能还有其他系统级别的配置\n\n让我整理一个清晰的迁移步骤。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，胖子！OpenClaw已经安装配置好了，迁移步骤如下：\n\n---\n\n## 📦 OpenClaw 迁移指南\n\n### 一、在旧电脑上打包备份\n\n**1. 打包 OpenClaw 配置目录**\n\n```powershell\n# 创建备份目录\nmkdir C:\\openclaw-backup\n\n# 复制配置\nCopy-Item -Path ~/.openclaw -Destination C:\\openclaw-backup\\.openclaw -Recurse\n\n# 压缩成 zip（可选）\nCompress-Archive -Path C:\\openclaw-backup\\.openclaw -DestinationPath C:\\openclaw-backup.zip\n```\n\n**2. 备份 npm 全局包（skillhub等）**\n\n```powershell\n# 查看 npm 全局包安装位置\nnpm config get prefix\n\n# 复制 npm 全局包\nCopy-Item -Path (npm root -g) -Destination C:\\openclaw-backup\\npm-global -Recurse\n```\n\n**3. 备份环境变量（如果有）**\n\n```powershell\n# 检查是否有 OpenClaw 相关环境变量\nGet-ChildItem Env: | Where-Object {$_.Name -like \"*OPENCLAW*\"}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 二、在新电脑上安装\n\n**1. 安装 Node.js（如果还没安装）**\n\n下载：https://nodejs.org/\n\n**2. 安装 OpenClaw**\n\n```powershell\nnpm install -g @sliverp/openclaw\n```\n\n**3. 恢复配置**\n\n```powershell\n# 从旧电脑复制 .openclaw 目录到新电脑\nCopy-Item -Path C:\\openclaw-backup\\.openclaw -Destination ~/.openclaw -Recurse\n```\n\n**4. 恢复 npm 全局包**\n\n```powershell\n# 恢复 skillhub 等全局包\nCopy-Item -Path C:\\openclaw-backup\\npm-global -Destination (npm root -g) -Recurse\n```\n\n**5. 重启 OpenClaw**\n\n```powershell\n# 停止旧服务（如果在运行）\nopenclaw gateway stop\n\n# 启动新服务\nopenclaw gateway start\n```\n\n---\n\n### 三、验证迁移\n\n```powershell\n# 检查状态\nopenclaw status\n\n# 检查已安装的插件\nopenclaw plugin list\n\n# 检查技能\nskillhub list\n```\n\n---\n\n### 四、关键文件说明\n\n| 目录/文件 | 说明 |\n|----------|------|\n| `~/.openclaw/` | 主配置目录 |\n| `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` | 核心配置文件 |\n| `~/.openclaw/workspace/` | 工作空间（包含 MEMORY.md、IDENTITY.md 等）|\n| `~/.openclaw/memory/` | 记忆文件 |\n| `~/.openclaw/extensions/` | 插件目录（qqbot等）|\n| `~/.openclaw/cron/` | 定时任务配置 |\n| `~/.openclaw/identity/` | 身份配置 |\n\n---\n\n### 五、注意事项\n\n1. **路径问题**：如果用户名不同，`~/.openclaw` 中的绝对路径可能需要更新（比如 `C:\\Users\\Administrator\\...` 改为新电脑的用户名）\n\n2. **插件重新安装**：某些插件可能需要在新电脑上重新初始化\n\n3. **认证信息**：QQbot的认证信息已包含在 `openclaw.json` 中，会自动迁移\n\n4. **测试**：迁移后先测试主要功能是否正常\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你创建一个自动化迁移脚本吗？或者有其他问题？😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":594,"output":949,"cacheRead":93525,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95068,"cost":{"input":0.0003564,"output":0.0020878,"cacheRead":0.01028775,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.012731949999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773111344984}}
{"type":"message","id":"cdf300ab","parentId":"25944bca","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:56:37.878Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"ROBOT1.0_HKbUeyU.6zOKuwCsaNsfMb55YTH-H-mEg36nLU3pbjGyYREpVdSBoy7YH-XDI0zxcLSeXyktKl5RlpWzn8cc3wjlj6H3wBCAbx3PilKrAso!\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\",\n  \"sender\": \"DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 10:57 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\",\n  \"id\": \"DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\"\n}\n```\n\n你正在通过 QQ 与用户对话。\n\n【会话上下文】\n- 用户: 未知 (DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8)\n- 场景: 私聊\n- 消息ID: ROBOT1.0_HKbUeyU.6zOKuwCsaNsfMb55YTH-H-mEg36nLU3pbjGyYREpVdSBoy7YH-XDI0zxcLSeXyktKl5RlpWzn8cc3wjlj6H3wBCAbx3PilKrAso!\n- 投递目标: qqbot:c2c:DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\n- 当前时间戳(ms): 1773111397586\n- 定时提醒投递地址: channel=qqbot, to=qqbot:c2c:DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\n\n【发送图片 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发图方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqimg>URL</qqimg>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"龙虾来啦！🦞 <qqimg>https://picsum.photos/800/600</qqimg>\"\n3. 图片来源: 已知URL直接用、用户发过的本地路径、也可以通过 web_search 搜索图片URL后使用\n4. ⚠️ 必须在文字回复中嵌入 <qqimg> 标签，禁止只调 tool 不回复文字（用户看不到任何内容）\n5. 不要说\"无法发送图片\"，直接用 <qqimg> 标签发\n\n【发送语音 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发语音方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvoice>本地音频文件路径</qqvoice>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"来听听吧！ <qqvoice>/tmp/tts/voice.mp3</qqvoice>\"\n3. 支持格式: .silk, .slk, .slac, .amr, .wav, .mp3, .ogg, .pcm\n4. ⚠️ <qqvoice> 只用于语音文件，图片请用 <qqimg>；两者不要混用\n5. 可以同时发送文字和语音，系统会按顺序投递\n6. ⚠️ 插件 TTS 未配置: 如果你有 TTS 工具（如 audio_speech），仍可用它生成音频文件后用 <qqvoice> 发送；若无 TTS 工具，则无法主动生成语音\n7. 语音识别未配置（STT），无法自动转录用户的语音消息\n\n【发送文件 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发文件方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqfile>文件路径或URL</qqfile>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"这是你要的文档 <qqfile>/tmp/report.pdf</qqfile>\"\n3. 支持: 本地文件路径、公网 URL\n4. 适用于非图片非语音的文件（如 pdf, docx, xlsx, zip, txt 等）\n5. ⚠️ 图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，其他文件用 <qqfile>\n\n【发送视频 - 必须遵守】\n1. 发视频方法: 在回复文本中写 <qqvideo>路径或URL</qqvideo>，系统自动处理\n2. 示例: \"<qqvideo>https://example.com/video.mp4</qqvideo>\" 或 \"<qqvideo>/path/to/video.mp4</qqvideo>\"\n3. 支持: 公网 URL、本地文件路径（系统自动读取上传）\n4. ⚠️ 视频用 <qqvideo>，图片用 <qqimg>，语音用 <qqvoice>，文件用 <qqfile>\n\n需要"}],"timestamp":1773111397871}}
{"type":"message","id":"2e1b9dbb","parentId":"cdf300ab","timestamp":"2026-03-10T02:57:57.676Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求创建自动化迁移脚本。我需要创建一个PowerShell脚本来备份和迁移OpenClaw配置。\n\n脚本应该包括：\n1. 备份功能：在旧电脑上打包所有必要的文件\n2. 恢复功能：在新电脑上恢复配置\n3. 验证功能：检查迁移是否成功\n\n让我创建这个脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，胖子！我帮你创建一个自动化迁移脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bfcc604d58da4af2a316385c","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\openclaw-migrate.ps1","content":"# OpenClaw 迁移脚本\n# 使用方法：\n#   旧电脑：.\\openclaw-migrate.ps1 backup\n#   新电脑：.\\openclaw-migrate.ps1 restore <backup-zip-path>\n\nparam(\n    [Parameter(Mandatory=$true)]\n    [ValidateSet(\"backup\", \"restore\")]\n    [string]$Action,\n\n    [Parameter(ParameterSetName=\"restore\", Mandatory=$true)]\n    [string]$BackupPath\n)\n\n# 配置\n$BackupDir = \"C:\\openclaw-backup\"\n$ConfigDir = Join-Path $env:USERPROFILE \".openclaw\"\n$ZipPath = \"$BackupDir\\openclaw-backup_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss').zip\"\n\nfunction Backup-OpenClaw {\n    Write-Host \"=== 开始备份 OpenClaw 配置 ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n    # 创建备份目录\n    if (-not (Test-Path $BackupDir)) {\n        New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $BackupDir | Out-Null\n        Write-Host \"✓ 创建备份目录: $BackupDir\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    }\n\n    # 备份配置目录\n    Write-Host \"✓ 备份配置目录: $ConfigDir\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Copy-Item -Path $ConfigDir -Destination \"$BackupDir\\.openclaw\" -Recurse -Force\n\n    # 备份 npm 全局包\n    $npmGlobalPath = npm root -g\n    if ($npmGlobalPath) {\n        Write-Host \"✓ 备份 npm 全局包: $npmGlobalPath\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n        Copy-Item -Path $npmGlobalPath -Destination \"$BackupDir\\npm-global\" -Recurse -Force\n    }\n\n    # 备份环境变量\n    Write-Host \"✓ 备份环境变量\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    $envVars = Get-ChildItem Env: | Where-Object {$_.Name -like \"*OPENCLAW*\"} | Select-Object Name, Value\n    $envVars | Export-Csv -Path \"$BackupDir\\environment.csv\" -NoTypeInformation -Encoding UTF8\n\n    # 创建说明文件\n    $readme = @\"\nOpenClaw 配置备份\n==================\n\n备份时间: $(Get-Date -Format 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss')\n原电脑: $env:COMPUTERNAME\n原用户: $env:USERNAME\n\n目录说明:\n- .openclaw/     : OpenClaw 主配置目录\n- npm-global/      : npm 全局包（包含 skillhub 等）\n- environment.csv  : 环境变量备份\n\n在新电脑上恢复:\n1. 复制 .openclaw 目录到新电脑的 $env:USERPROFILE\\.openclaw\n2. 复制 npm-global 目录到新电脑的 npm 全局包位置\n3. 导入环境变量（如果需要）\n4. 运行: openclaw gateway restart\n\"@\n    $readme | Out-File -FilePath \"$BackupDir\\README.txt\" -Encoding UTF8\n\n    # 压缩\n    Write-Host \"✓ 创建压缩包...\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Compress-Archive -Path \"$BackupDir\\*\" -DestinationPath $ZipPath -Force\n\n    # 清理临时文件\n    Remove-Item \"$BackupDir\\.openclaw\" -Recurse -Force\n    if (Test-Path \"$BackupDir\\npm-global\") {\n        Remove-Item \"$BackupDir\\npm-global\" -Recurse -Force\n    }\n\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"=== 备份完成 ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    Write-Host \"备份文件: $ZipPath\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"大小: $((Get-Item $ZipPath).Length / 1MB) MB\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"将此文件复制到新电脑，然后运行:\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Write-Host \"  .\\openclaw-migrate.ps1 restore `\"$ZipPath`\"\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n}\n\nfunction Restore-OpenClaw {\n    Write-Host \"=== 开始恢复 OpenClaw 配置 ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n\n    # 检查备份文件\n    if (-not (Test-Path $BackupPath)) {\n        Write-Host \"✗ 备份文件不存在: $BackupPath\" -ForegroundColor Red\n        exit 1\n    }\n\n    Write-Host \"✓ 解压备份文件: $BackupPath\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n    # 解压到临时目录\n    $tempDir = Join-Path $env:TEMP \"openclaw-restore_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMddHHmmss')\"\n    Expand-Archive -Path $BackupPath -DestinationPath $tempDir -Force\n\n    # 恢复配置目录\n    $backupConfigDir = Join-Path $tempDir \".openclaw\"\n    if (Test-Path $backupConfigDir) {\n        Write-Host \"✓ 恢复配置目录\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n\n        # 停止 OpenClaw Gateway\n        Write-Host \"  → 停止 OpenClaw Gateway...\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n        try {\n            openclaw gateway stop 2>&1 | Out-Null\n        } catch {}\n\n        # 备份现有配置\n        if (Test-Path $ConfigDir) {\n            $existingBackup = \"$ConfigDir.backup_$(Get-Date -Format 'yyyyMMdd_HHmmss')\"\n            Write-Host \"  → 备份现有配置到: $existingBackup\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n            Copy-Item -Path $ConfigDir -Destination $existingBackup -Recurse\n        }\n\n        # 恢复配置\n        Copy-Item -Path $backupConfigDir -Destination $ConfigDir -Recurse -Force\n        Write-Host \"  ✓ 配置已恢复到: $ConfigDir\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    }\n\n    # 恢复 npm 全局包\n    $backupNpmDir = Join-Path $tempDir \"npm-global\"\n    if (Test-Path $backupNpmDir) {\n        $npmGlobalPath = npm root -g\n        if ($npmGlobalPath) {\n            Write-Host \"✓ 恢复 npm 全局包\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n            Copy-Item -Path \"$backupNpmDir\\*\" -Destination $npmGlobalPath -Recurse -Force\n            Write-Host \"  ✓ npm 全局包已恢复\" -ForegroundColor Green\n        }\n    }\n\n    # 显示环境变量\n    $envFile = Join-Path $tempDir \"environment.csv\"\n    if (Test-Path $envFile) {\n        Write-Host \"✓ 环境变量备份:\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n        Get-Content $envFile | Select-Object -Skip 1 | ForEach-Object {\n            if ($_.Trim()) {\n                Write-Host \"  $_\" -ForegroundColor Gray\n            }\n        }\n    }\n\n    # 清理临时文件\n    Remove-Item $tempDir -Recurse -Force\n\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"=== 恢复完成 ===\" -ForegroundColor Green\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"接下来的步骤:\" -ForegroundColor Cyan\n    Write-Host \"  1. 重启终端（确保环境变量生效）\" -ForegroundColor White\n    Write-Host \"  2. 验证配置: openclaw status\" -ForegroundColor White\n    Write-Host \"  3. 启动服务: openclaw gateway start\" -ForegroundColor White\n    Write-Host \"  4. 检查插件: openclaw plugin list\" -ForegroundColor White\n    Write-Host \"\"\n    Write-Host \"⚠️ 注意: 如果用户名不同，可能需要更新配置中的绝对路径\" -ForegroundColor Yellow\n}\n\n# 执行操作\nswitch ($Action) {\n    \"backup\" {\n        Backup-OpenClaw\n    }\n    \"restore\" {\n        Restore-OpenClaw\n    }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":3031,"output":1922,"cacheRead":92893,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97846,"cost":{"input":0.0018185999999999999,"output":0.0042284,"cacheRead":0.01021823,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01626523}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773111397876}}
