{"type":"message","id":"323dc7ad","parentId":"260410ba","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:23:42.329Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e4066ba784354a7496f61f20","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: tavily\ndescription: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API. Returns concise, relevant results for AI agents.\nhomepage: https://tavily.com\nmetadata: {\"clawdbot\":{\"emoji\":\"🔍\",\"requires\":{\"bins\":[\"node\"],\"env\":[\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"]},\"primaryEnv\":\"TAVILY_API_KEY\"}}\n---\n\n# Tavily Search\n\nAI-optimized web search using Tavily API. Designed for AI agents - returns clean, relevant content.\n\n## Search\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\"\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" -n 10\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --deep\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/search.mjs \"query\" --topic news\n```\n\n## Options\n\n- `-n <count>`: Number of results (default: 5, max: 20)\n- `--deep`: Use advanced search for deeper research (slower, more comprehensive)\n- `--topic <topic>`: Search topic - `general` (default) or `news`\n- `--days <n>`: For news topic, limit to last n days\n\n## Extract content from URL\n\n```bash\nnode {baseDir}/scripts/extract.mjs \"https://example.com/article\"\n```\n\nNotes:\n- Needs `TAVILY_API_KEY` from https://tavily.com\n- Tavily is optimized for AI - returns clean, relevant snippets\n- Use `--deep` for complex research questions\n- Use `--topic news` for current events\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773113022321}}
{"type":"message","id":"9caacd90","parentId":"323dc7ad","timestamp":"2026-03-10T03:24:18.727Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"完美！tavily 技能已经成功安装。这是一个 AI 优化的网络搜索技能，使用 Tavily API。\n\n技能已安装到：C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.claude\\skills\\tavily\n\n不过我注意到这个技能需要 TAVILY_API_KEY 环境变量。我应该告诉用户这一点。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"胖子，tavily-search技能安装成功！✅"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e840aabff7af438abf671ec2","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\技能安装记录.md","content":"# 技能安装记录\n\n## 已安装技能\n\n### 1. tavily\n- **安装时间**: 2026-03-10\n- **安装路径**: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.claude\\skills\\tavily\n- **功能**: AI-optimized web search via Tavily API\n- **使用方法**: 该技能会自动激活，当识别到相关搜索需求时使用\n\n### 配置要求\n需要设置环境变量 `TAVILY_API_KEY`：\n\n1. 获取 API Key: 访问 https://tavily.com\n2. 设置环境变量:\n   ```powershell\n   # Windows 临时设置（当前会话有效）\n   $env:TAVILY_API_KEY = \"your-api-key\"\n\n   # Windows 永久设置\n   [System.Environment]::SetEnvironmentVariable('TAVILY_API_KEY', 'your-api-key', 'User')\n   ```\n\n### 功能说明\n- **常规搜索**: 返回简洁、相关的结果\n- **深度搜索**: 使用高级搜索进行深度研究（更慢但更全面）\n- **新闻搜索**: 搜索最新资讯\n- **结果数量**: 默认5条，最多20条\n\n### 使用场景\n- 网络搜索\n- 内容提取\n- 新闻检索\n- 复杂研究问题\n\n---\n\n## SkillHub 状态\n- **已安装**: skillhub CLI 工具\n- **安装方式**: npm install -g skillhub\n- **安装位置**: C:\\Users\\Administrator\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm\\skillhub.ps1\n\n### 已安装的技能\n1. tavily (AI-optimized web search)\n2. carmandale/agent-config/self-improving-agent (self-improving agent - 安装失败)\n\n### 技能搜索命令\n```bash\n# 搜索技能\nskillhub search <keyword>\n\n# 安装技能\nskillhub install <skill-id>\n\n# 列出已安装技能\nskillhub list\n```\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":346,"output":601,"cacheRead":100593,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":101540,"cost":{"input":0.00020759999999999998,"output":0.0013222000000000002,"cacheRead":0.01106523,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01259503}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17