{"type":"message","id":"21364706","parentId":"82cf5805","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:37:41.311Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户再次询问明天厦门的天气。之前的尝试都因为网络超时失败了。让我再试试看能否获取到天气信息。\n\n我可以尝试用Open-Meteo API，这是一个免费的天气API，不需要API key。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"胖子，让我再试试用其他方式查厦门天气："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b05c5a41743442b6994f8ec0","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport urllib.request\nimport json\n\nurl = 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=24.4798&longitude=118.0894&daily=temperature_2m_max,precipitation_sum,weathercode&timezone=Asia%2FShanghai'\ntry:\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    response = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=5)\n    data = json.loads(response.read())\n    \n    print('厦门天气预报')\n    print('='*20)\n    if 'daily' in data:\n        daily = data['daily']\n        for i, day in enumerate(daily[:2]):  # 今天和明天\n            date = day.get('time', '')[:10]\n            max_temp = day.get('temperature_2m_max', {}).get('day', 0)\n            precip = day.get('precipitation_sum', 0)\n            code = day.get('weathercode', 0)\n            \n            if i == 0:\n                print(f'今天 ({date}):')\n                print(f'  最高温度: {max_temp}°C')\n            else:\n                print(f'明天 ({date}):')\n                print(f'  最高温度: {max_temp}°C')\n                print(f'  降水量: {precip}mm')\n                \n                # 天气代码说明\n                if 0 <= code < 3:\n                    desc = '晴'\n                elif code < 50:\n                    desc = '多云'\n                elif code < 70:\n                    desc = '阴'\n                elif code < 80:\n                    desc = '小雨'\n                else:\n                    desc = '雨天'\n                print(f'  天气: {desc}')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'查询失败: {e}')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model