{"type":"message","id":"98ee5f2b","parentId":"ff7cbdb7","timestamp":"2026-03-10T08:05:28.756Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了，openai-whisper 已经安装好了。现在让我尝试转录音频文件。\n\n文件路径是：C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\qqbot\\downloads\\合伙企业会议_1773129780541.m4a\n\n注意：这是 .m4a 文件，是微信使用的 SILK 音频编码格式。Whisper 可能无法直接识别这种格式，需要转换成 .wav 或 .mp3。\n\n让我尝试直接转录，看看能否识别。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了，openai-whisper 安装成功！✅ 现在让我帮你转录音频："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ab904c87cb364943a15bfe3f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport whisper\n\n# 加载 Whisper 模型（使用 base 模型）\nprint('正在加载 Whisper 模型（首次可能需要下载）...')\nmodel = whisper.load_model('base')\nprint('模型加载完成！')\n\n# 转录音频文件\naudio_path = r'C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\qqbot\\downloads\\合伙企业会议_1773129780541.m4a'\n\nprint(f'正在转录音频文件...')\nprint(f'文件路径: {audio_path}')\n\ntry:\n    # 尝试转录\n    result = model.transcribe(audio_path, language='zh')\n    \n    print('')\n    print('=== 转录结果 ===')\n    print(result['text'])\n    \nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'转录失败: {e}')\n    import traceback\n    traceback.print_exc()\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":412,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137625,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0009064,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0832342}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773129893397}}
