{"type":"message","id":"84451665","parentId":"beff473d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T08:06:20.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看来 torch 库有问题，无法加载 DLL。这可能是因为缺少一些系统依赖，或者是 GPU 相关的库不兼容。\n\n让我尝试另一个方法：使用 ffmpeg 将 .m4a 转换成 .wav，然后用简单的音频处理库来转录。\n\n或者，我可以给用户一个 Python 脚本，让用户在自己的环境中运行。\n\n不过先让我检查一下是否有其他更简单的方案。\n\n或者，我可以直接告诉用户当前的问题，并给出解决方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"胖子，遇到了一些技术问题。😅\n\n---\n\n## 🎤 遇到的问题\n\n**OpenAI Whisper 转录失败**：系统缺少依赖，无法加载 PyTorch 库\n\n---\n\n## 💡 解决方案\n\n我给你写一个 Python 转录脚本，你可以在自己的电脑上运行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7772ab5793e14af4a3ad0671","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 音频转录脚本\n# 安装依赖后运行：pip install openai-whisper\n\nimport whisper\nimport sys\n\ndef transcribe_audio(audio_file, model_size='base'):\n    \"\"\"\n    转录音频文件为文字\n    \n    参数:\n        audio_file: 音频文件路径\n        model_size: 模型大小（tiny/base/small/medium/large/turbo）\n                   turbo 最快，base 推荐\n    \"\"\"\n    \n    print(f'正在加载 Whisper 模型 ({model_size})...')\n    model = whisper.load_model(model_size)\n    \n    print(f'正在转录音频: {audio_file}')\n    print('这可能需要几分钟，请耐心等待...')\n    \n    result = model.transcribe(audio_file, language='zh')\n    \n    print('')\n    print('=== 转录结果 ===')\n    print(result['text'])\n    print('')\n    \n    # 如果需要详细的时间戳\n    print('详细分段:')\n    for segment in result['segments']:\n        start = f\"{segment['start']:.2f}\"\n        end = f\"{segment['end']:.2f}\"\n        print(f\"[{start}s - {end}s] {segment['text']}\")\n    \n    return result['text']\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    if len(sys.argv) < 2:\n        print('用法: python transcribe.py <音频文件路径>')\n        print('示例: python transcribe.py meeting.m4a')\n        print('示例: python transcribe.py meeting.mp3')\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    audio_file = sys.argv[1]\n    transcribe_audio(audio_file, model_size='base')\n","path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\transcribe.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":625,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137838,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.0013750000000000001,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0837028}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773129931364}}
