{"type":"message","id":"363e28f8","parentId":"5bfbf534","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:11:29.257Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问\"明天天气怎么样\"，这是关于天气的询问。\n\n从之前的对话来看：\n1. 我之前尝试查询厦门天气，但遇到了网络超时问题\n2. 我已经安装了weather技能\n3. 现在是2026年3月10日，明天是3月11日\n\n现在我可以尝试使用weather技能来查询明天的天气。但是之前搜索天气时遇到了网络问题。\n\n让我尝试使用已安装的weather技能来查询厦门明天的天气。\n\n根据之前的经验：\n- wttr.in API 访问一直超时\n- Open-Meteo API 之前成功获取了数据\n\n让我再尝试用Open-Meteo查询明天厦门的天气。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，胖子！让我查询一下明天（3月11日）厦门的天气："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_04d5795477e246a89eb628e3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python -c \"\nimport urllib.request\nimport json\n\nurl = 'https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude=24.4798&longitude=118.0894&daily=temperature_2m_max,temperature_2m_min,precipitation_sum,weathercode&timezone=Asia%2FShanghai'\ntry:\n    req = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0'})\n    response = urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10)\n    data = json.loads(response.read())\n    \n    print('厦门明天天气预报 (2026年3月11日)')\n    print('='*40)\n    \n    if 'daily' in data and len(data['daily']) > 1:\n        tomorrow = data['daily'][1]\n        date = tomorrow.get('time', '')[:10]\n        max_temp = tomorrow.get('temperature_2m_max', {}).get('day', 0)\n        min_temp = tomorrow.get('temperature_2m_min', {}).get('day', 0)\n        precip = tomorrow.get('precipitation_sum', 0)\n        code = tomorrow.get('weathercode', 0)\n        \n        print(f'日期: {date}')\n        print(f'最高温度: {max_temp}°C')\n        print(f'最低温度: {min_temp}°C')\n        print(f'降水量: {precip}mm')\n        \n        # 天气描述\n        if 0 <= code < 3:\n            weather = '晴'\n        elif code < 50:\n            weather = '多云'\n        elif code < 70:\n            weather = '阴'\n        elif code < 80:\n            weather = '小雨'\n        elif code < 100:\n            weather = '中雨'\n        else:\n            weather = '雨天'\n        \n        print(f'天气: {weather}')\n        print('='*40)\n        \n        # 建议\n        print('穿衣建议: 温度适中，建议穿薄外套或长袖')\n        \n        if code < 50:\n            print('活动建议: 天气不错，适合户外活动')\n        elif code < 70:\n            print('活动建议: 阴天，建议室内活动或备雨具')\n        else:\n            print('活动建议: 有雨，记得带伞！')\nexcept Exception as e:\n    print(f'查询失败: {e}')\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":137213,"output":815,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138028,"cost":{"input":0.08232779999999999,"output":0.001793,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0841208}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773144661746}}
